# <type>(<scope>): <subject>
#
# <body>
#
# <footer>

# Type: feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, perf, test, chore, ci
# Scope: Optional. Include scope to describe what is being modified (e.g., keywords, layout, api, auth)
# Subject: Concise description in present tense, max 50 characters

# Body: Explain what and why, not how. Wrap at 72 characters.
# Footer: Reference issues (Closes #123) or breaking changes (BREAKING CHANGE: ...)
